whereas.text:
Whereas an independent, unfettered media and freedom of expression, including the Internet and
			 social media, are essential elements of democratic, transparent, and open
			 societies;

Whereas the Government of Turkey imposed a countrywide ban on access to Twitter on March 20, 2014,
			 and to YouTube on March 27, 2014, blocking the use of the communications
			 platforms;

Whereas respected nongovernmental organizations have condemned the decision to block Twitter and
			 YouTube as an attack on Internet freedom and freedom of expression in
			 Turkey;
